{"tid":1972822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第卅肆期牆紙】這個時代是一個政治的時代","createTime":"2020-04-14T18:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T07:11:06.000Z","uid":253119,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"be4696dcf07b2379f4195ac43e223f1660d1d306","tid":1972822,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"政治無所不在，了解政治更成了每個香港人的必修一課。今期牆紙會帶大家由獨派看到建制，思考香港未來的政治格局。<br />\n<br />\n俗語有話：「喺邊度跌低，就喺邊度企返起身」。今期牆紙再接再厲，與大家一起加深對香港政治的認識，希望激發更多討論，還望各位多多指教。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 獨派的未來&mdash;&mdash;訪問香港民族陣線<br />\n2. 本土派的崛起與發展<br />\n3. 香港政治光譜加強版<br />\n4. 熱普城：真的是分化的代名詞？<br />\n5. 田「不」俊=真正建制派<br />\n6. 不要叫人小看你年輕<br />\n7. 毫無代價唱最幸福的歌？<br />\n8. 專訪HoKoGuide 負責人&mdash;&mdash;武漢肺炎下的良心消費新模式<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#34期 #34th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTAo7aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTAo7aa.jpg&h=17b6985b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYRLA3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYRLA3w.jpg&h=e421f2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reDmTQc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreDmTQc.jpg&h=6ef42992&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Oa09oy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Oa09oy.jpg&h=ba457618&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzL4RBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzL4RBU.jpg&h=10d4851d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YMcf3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YMcf3A.jpg&h=bd5cafec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbgcf3A.jpg